import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next'; import './i18n'; import LoanCalculator from './components/LoanCalculator'; import LanguageSwitcher from './components/LanguageSwitcher'; import StarryBackground from './components/StarryBackground'; import { LoanResult } from './utils/loanCalculator'; const App: React.FC = () => { const { t, i18n } = useTranslation(); const [result, setResult] = useState(null); const handleCalculate = (result: LoanResult) => { setResult(result); }; return (

{t('appTitle')}

{result && (

{t('result')}

{t('maxLoanAmount')}: AED {result.maxLoanAmount.toLocaleString()}
{t('maxLoanTerm')}: {result.maxLoanTerm} {t('years')}
{t('monthlyPayment')}: AED {result.monthlyPayment.toLocaleString()}
{t('totalMonthlyDebt')}: AED {result.totalMonthlyDebt.toLocaleString()}
{/* 转贷分析结果 */} {result.refinanceAnalysis && (

{t('refinanceAnalysis')}

{t('cashoutAmount')}: AED {result.refinanceAnalysis.cashoutAmount.toLocaleString()}
{t('monthlySavings')}: AED {result.refinanceAnalysis.monthlySavings.toLocaleString()}
{t('totalSavings')}: AED {result.refinanceAnalysis.totalSavings.toLocaleString()}
{t('netBenefit')}: AED {result.refinanceAnalysis.netBenefit.toLocaleString()}
{t('breakEvenMonths')}: {result.refinanceAnalysis.breakEvenMonths} {t('months')}
)}

{t('fees')}

{t('evaluationFee')}: AED {result.fees.evaluation.toLocaleString()}
{t('registrationFee')}: AED {result.fees.registration.toLocaleString()}
{t('transferFee')}: AED {result.fees.transfer.toLocaleString()}
{t('bankFee')}: AED {result.fees.bankFee.toLocaleString()}
{/* 转贷特有费用 */} {result.fees.earlyRepayment !== undefined && (
{t('earlyRepaymentFee')}: AED {result.fees.earlyRepayment.toLocaleString()}
)} {result.fees.mortgageDischarge !== undefined && (
{t('mortgageDischarge')}: AED {result.fees.mortgageDischarge.toLocaleString()}
)}
)}
); }; export default App;
